        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced shallot</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until slightly softened</p><p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1675779701018-x200.jpg",
