        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the shallot is slightly softened, add your <strong>curry powder</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> and <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong> to the dish with your <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong> and <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
