            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>white long grain rice</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> with 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong>, making sure all the rice is fully submerged</p><p>Cover very tightly with <strong>tin</strong> <strong>foil</strong> and put the dish in the oven for 30 min or until all the water is absorbed and the rice is cooked – this is your <strong>baked rice</strong></p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p><p>Wash your<strong> spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1675779728406-x200.jpg",
