    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>baked Bengali-Style mustard & coconut haddock curry</strong> with the <strong>baked rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Dig in!</p>",
